column2: SELECT f.objid, f.distance, p.ra AS rasdss, p.dec AS decsdss, p.psfMag_u as psfu, p.psfMag_g as psfg, p.psfMag_r as psfr, p.psfMag_i as psfi, p.psfMag_z as psfz, p.psfMagErr_u as eu, p.psfMagErr_g as eg, p.psfMagErr_r as er, p.psfMagErr_i as ei, p.psfMagErr_z as ez, p.modelMag_u, p.modelMagErr_u, p.modelMag_g, p.modelMagErr_g, p.modelMag_r, p.modelMagErr_r, p.modelMag_i, p.modelMagErr_i, p.modelMag_z, p.modelMagErr_z, p.mjd as mjd, p.extinction_u as au into mydb.MgII from mydb.galaxy_bright_optical AS m CROSS APPLY dbo.fGetNearbyObjAllEq (#, #, #/#) AS f JOIN PhotoObjall AS p ON f.objid = p.objid
